Submission made entirely by Stefan Candea, Animation assets imported from mixamo, and textures for the terrain have their respective sources in the folder.

The Goal of the project is to create low-poly cyberpunk palette experience, similar to a topdown 2.5D shooter


controls: 
Left mouse button - fire forward
Right mouse button - move player



I am aware that the raycast does not ignore the player and zombie, and will only function if you click on the floorplane tagged as "PlayArea"
